Shawn Pearce is a software engineering manager in Google's Open Source Programs Office, where he leads Git related tool development. After being a long-time contributor to the Git version control system, Shawn founded the EGit and JGit projects at Eclipse, and the Gerrit Code Review project as an off-shoot of the <a href="http://source.android.com/">Android Open Source Project</a>. At Google, Shawn and his team continue to develop innovative improvements for Git and Gerrit Code Review.
